{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">探索电荷间的相互作用。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">同种电荷相互排斥，异种电荷相互吸引。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">橡胶棒、毛皮、玻璃棒、丝绸、绝缘支架</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.用丝绸摩擦两根玻璃棒，并将其中一根支在绝缘支架上；</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.拖动另一根玻璃棒靠近放在绝缘支架上的玻璃棒，观察现象；</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">3.拖动毛皮摩擦橡胶棒；</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">4.拖动橡胶棒靠近放在绝缘支架上的玻璃棒，观察现象。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">同种电荷相互排斥，异种电荷相互吸引。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">用丝绸摩擦过的玻璃棒带正电；用毛皮摩擦过的橡胶棒带负电。</span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}